ZH: 这位大使已经到达了会议现场。
EN: The ambassador has arrived at the conference venue.

ZH: 那名大使正在就双方合作进行谈判。
EN: The ambassador is negotiating on cooperation between the two sides.

ZH: 大使表示愿意为提升双边关系做出努力。
EN: The ambassador expressed willingness to make efforts to enhance bilateral relations.

ZH: 大使馆发表了一份公开声明。
EN: The embassy issued a public statement.

ZH: 大使与当地政府进行了交流。
EN: The ambassador had discussions with the local government.

ZH: 大使向国内媒体透露了一些重要消息。
EN: The ambassador revealed some important news to the domestic media.

ZH: 大使已经被任命为驻外使节。
EN: The ambassador has been appointed as an envoy to a foreign country.

ZH: 这位大使定期与外交部保持联系。
EN: This ambassador maintains regular contact with the foreign ministry.

ZH: 大使是外交官中的代表人物。
EN: Ambassadors are representative figures in diplomatic circles.

ZH: 大使代表了其国家的利益。
EN: Ambassadors represent the interests of their countries.

ZH: 大使能够发挥重要的调解作用。
EN: Ambassadors can play important mediating roles.

ZH: 这是我第一次见到这位大使。
EN: This is the first time I have met this ambassador.

ZH: 大使事务还有许多工作需要处理。
EN: There is still a lot of work to be done in the ambassador's office.

ZH: 大使与外交人员齐心协力，推动了一项重要协议。
EN: The ambassador, together with diplomatic personnel, pushed forward an important agreement.

ZH: 这位大使为维护和平作出了卓越贡献。
EN: The ambassador has made outstanding contributions to maintaining peace.

ZH: 大使在外交领域具有广泛的影响力。
EN: The ambassador has wide influence in the field of diplomacy.

ZH: 这位大使对两国之间的友好关系作出了重要贡献。
EN: This ambassador has made important contributions to the friendly relations between the two countries.

ZH: 大使的工作需要克服许多困难。
EN: The ambassador's work requires overcoming many difficulties.

ZH: 大使代表着国家的形象。
EN: Ambassadors represent the image of their countries.

ZH: 这名大使正在拜访多个国家，推动国际合作。
EN: This ambassador is visiting multiple countries to promote international cooperation.
